Input: Text
Output: 3 files
  - Video at normal speed
  - Video at 0.75 speed
  - Video by word-by-word
Flow:
  - Send request to for version 1 and 2 to amazon
    - marks file
    - audio file
  - Send request to for version 3 to amazon
    - marks file
    - audio file
  - create images from text
  - generate input of ffmeg for version 1
  - generate video of version 1
  - run sox to generate slower audio
  - generate input of ffmeg for version 2
  - generate video of version 2
  - generate input of ffmeg for version 3
  - generate video of version 3
